@subsubsection Arithmetic operations


@deffn Procedure + @vari{z} @dots{}
@deffnx Procedure * @vari{z} @dots{}
These procedures return the sum or product of their arguments.

@example
(+ 3 4)                                =>  7
(+ 3)                                  =>  3
(+)                                    =>  0
